    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Christian clergy whose defining official function is to hear the confessions of others, prescribes penance, and grants absolution. Prime examples are the private spiritual directors of a king or other great personage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
